\prod_{k=1}^n \cos\left(\frac{x}{2^k}\right) = \frac{1}{2^n} \prod_{k=0}^{n-1} \left(z^{2^k}+z^{-2^k}\right) = \frac{1}{2^n} z^{-\sum_{k=0}^{n-1} 2^k}  \prod_{k=0}^{n-1} \left(z^{2^{k+1}}+1\right)\\ = \frac{1}{2^n} z^{1-2^n} \frac{1}{z+1} \prod_{k=0}^n \left(z^{2^k}+1\right).
\frac{1}{2^n} z^{1-2^n} \frac{1}{z+1} \left(1+z+z^2+\cdots+z^{2^{n+1}-1}\right) = \frac{1}{2^n} z^{1-2^n} \frac{1}{z+1} \frac{1-z^{2^{n+1}}}{1-z}\\ = \frac{1}{2^n} \frac{1}{z+1} \frac{z^{1-2^n}-z^{1+2^n}}{1-z} = \frac{1}{2^n} \frac{z}{z+1} \frac{z^{-2^n}-z^{2^n}}{1-z} = \frac{1}{2^n} z \frac{z^{-2^n}-z^{2^n}}{1-z^2} \\ = \frac{1}{2^n} \frac{z^{-2^n}-z^{2^n}}{1/z-z} = \frac{1}{2^n}  \frac{\sin(x)}{\sin(x/2^n)} = \frac{x/2^n}{\sin(x/2^n)} \frac{\sin(x)}{x}.
